Do they know who you are in the pits of hell?

00:47:30.260 --> 00:47:38.942
Fight from a place of full, not from a place of empty.

00:47:38.942 --> 00:47:42.367
Well, glory to God!

00:47:42.367 --> 00:47:46.555
Thank you for joining me today, y'all.

00:47:46.555 --> 00:47:48.571
We're making a difference.

00:47:48.571 --> 00:47:55.215
May His face shine on you and give you peace today.

00:47:55.215 --> 00:48:00.484
In this Christmas season, we say, 'Happy birthday, Jesus!

00:48:00.484 --> 00:48:05.027
' We sing 'Happy Birthday' to Him, or even that Stevie Wonder song: 'Happy birthday to you.

00:48:05.027 --> 00:48:08.944
' Stevie Wonder's is a happy song—it's fun!

00:48:08.944 --> 00:48:16.899
We play it every year and say, 'Jesus, it's your birthday!

00:48:16.899 --> 00:48:25.915
' Tomorrow I'll talk to you all more about the thousand-year reign and what we do after it.

00:48:29.387 --> 00:48:35.070
The Lord Jesus is coming and He has a mansion for you.

00:48:35.070 --> 00:48:46.050
He was showing me the depth of the martyr's crown and how much of an honor it is in heaven.

00:48:46.050 --> 00:48:56.955
He showed me a man who sowed in secret a lot—he gave away over $53 million but never once wanted recognition.

00:48:59.590 --> 00:49:04.520
The Lord showed me his robe in heaven, breathtaking with gold designs.

00:49:04.520 --> 00:49:34.773
If you get praise for it on this side, there's no blessing like that on the other side.

00:49:34.773 --> 00:50:04.794
You're going to be amazed that it's the little granny in the corner who gave her widow's mite, who interceded for the preacher.

00:50:04.794 --> 00:50:18.195
The last will be first and the first will be last.

00:50:18.195 --> 00:50:27.880
If you want to hear God the most, go clean a toilet!

00:50:27.880 --> 00:50:31.745
There's something beautiful in it.

00:50:31.745 --> 00:50:44.920
I did that for 15 years—some of the nastiest things you'll ever see, like cleaning up diarrhea when people would mess themselves.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.200
But I learned how to truly worship Him in those hard times.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.050
He became real.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.900
Well, I pray this video blessed you and put a smile on your face.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.550
Jesus loves you so much, and we will see you all again tomorrow.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.800
Praise the Lord, y'all have a great night.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.000
Bye-bye.
